| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0845 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e1cc0292-4541-51e1-9c8a-2be7b3f0fd43"
